<p><strong>标题：</strong>SCP-2080-JP - 旧时的种子<br />
<strong>作者：</strong>©︎<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nonsapereaude" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6762143); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6762143&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609147381" alt="NonSapereAude" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6762143)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nonsapereaude" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6762143); return false;">NonSapereAude</a></span><br />
<strong>译者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/backlight-sh" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5374263); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5374263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609147381" alt="Backlight SH" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5374263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/backlight-sh" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5374263); return false;">Backlight SH</a></span><br />
<strong>校订：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/snoj" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3266034); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3266034&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609147381" alt="snoj" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3266034)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/snoj" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3266034); return false;">snoj</a></span><br />
<strong>发布年份：</strong>2020</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
